  "title": "Full Stack Developer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilites</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Primarily involve in software programming based on specifications.</li>\n  <li>Application Software Unit and Integration Testing</li>\n  <li>Assist in software implementation and user acceptance</li>\n  <li>Update the User Manual, Functional &amp; Design documentation</li>\n  <li>Perform application and end user support for projects under maintenance</li>\n  <li> Experience in MS SQL Server &amp; MS SQL Reporting Service.</li>\n  <li>Hand-on programming in Visual Studio C# .NET 1.1/2.0 and above (WinForms).</li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge and working experience of object-oriented design and development methodology.</li>\n  <li>Strong analytical, problem solving and documentation skills.</li>\n  <li>Good interpersonal skills with strong team spirit. Must be able to function well as a team member in a project and sourcing for technical solution independently.</li>\n  <li>Experience in Banking/Remittance industry shall be advantageous</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Mandatory Skills:C-Sharp, ASP.NET, CLIENT SIDE SCRIPT, JAVA SCRIPT, FRAMEWORK - CORE SKILL - Resource should be an Individual contributor. Leadership qualities, communications. Change catalyst, and new tech.</li>\n  <li><strong>Experience in Angular JS, JQuery, KNOCK OUT, AJAX, MVC, site minder is a must.</strong></li>\n  <li>Must be Versed with the latest trends in .Net Technology.</li>\n</ul>",
